title: Enjoy Spacious Two Bed/Two Bath + Rooftop Pool And Spa!
posting_body: ['The Jessica', '1611 N Formosa, Hollywood, CA, 90046', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Hollywood Apartment Communities', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1131 Sq.', 'Ft.', "Hollywood's best views can be enjoyed at The Jessica, from these contemporary Hollywood apartments.", 'Located between Hollywood and Sunset Boulevards, all of the excitement of Hollywood is right at your doorstep.', 'Walk to famous restaurants and nearby shops or come home to relax by the rooftop pool and spa.', 'End your day with a workout in our fitness center.', 'Select upgraded units offer shaker style cabinetry, granite countertops, and contemporary fixtures.', 'Multiple floor plan options are available.', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.', 'Please contact our leasing office for current pricing and specials.', 'Features', '- Shaker Style Cabinetry', '- Granite Counter tops', '- Private Balconies and Patios', '- Contemporary Fixtures', '- Tech Ready', '- Dishwasher', '- New Appliances', '- Central Air/Heating', '- Garbage Disposal', '- Fully Renovated Upscale Units', '- Fireplace', '- Breakfast Bars', '- Secure Parking', 'Community Amenities', '- Near Everything', '- Controlled Access Parking', '- Gated Access', '- Fitness Center', '- Soothing Spa/Hot Tub', '- Rooftop Pool', '- Laundry Facilities', 'Pet Policy', 'Please Contact us!', 'Photos displayed are a representation of the community but may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Availability and rental rates are updated daily, and conditions are subject to change without notice.', 'Please contact the property for current availability and pricing.', 'zNdGZn3Ql5l']
